{"title":"访罗诗稿（五首）","authors":["杨应彬"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访罗诗稿（五首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨应彬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国庆观礼（武陵春）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百里长街人攒涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风送满城芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤帜如潮花似海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神采倍飞扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十六年迈大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利益辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦绣前程谁保卫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭紧握手中枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞维尔恰（虞美人）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山碧树秋光好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"极目多芳草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红楼掩映绿丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院繁花竞放傲西风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中罗地隔万千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海外存知己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主人好客客心欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝愿人民友谊万千年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞花城科特列亚市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花城日日泛花潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩蕊繁芳处处娇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石竹竞同玫瑰艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风更喜上眉梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游斯纳哥夫湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋水涵林林接天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿杨摇曳水云间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻舟载得情如许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破浪乘风任往还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在罗马尼亚喜闻中国音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在罗期间数次在宴会上听到罗音乐家为中罗友谊演奏中国音乐，感极赋此。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九千里外动乡心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乍闻浑似伯牙琴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同是环球革命者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相逢何处不知音！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}